snippet.title: Ultra Kaiju Monster Rancher - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Mark your calendars and get ready for some time on the ranch with your Ultra Kaiju when Ultra Kaiju Monster Rancher launches on 20 October 2022!

Exclusive bonus content lie in wait for those who get the game early, so don't miss out 👀

#UltraKaijuMonsterRancher #BandaiNamco
